snippet: A 22-year-old woman who tried to give her newborn to authorities by pretending to find the baby on a Hawaii beach kept her pregnancy a secret because she didn't want to disappoint her family, her attorney said....

headline.print_headline: Honolulu Mom Who Lied About Baby Is Sentenced
headline.main: Honolulu Mom Who Lied About Baby Is Sentenced

lead_paragraph: A 22-year-old woman who tried to give her newborn to authorities by pretending to find the baby on a Hawaii beach kept her pregnancy a secret because she didn't want to disappoint her family, her attorney said.
